data.description: Introducing a charming unit in the Preserve at Weaver Creek! This delightful property offers a warm and inviting interior with a blend of carpet and wood floors in all the right places. The living room welcomes you with a cozy fireplace, perfect for chilly evenings spent relaxing with loved ones. The kitchen is a standout feature, boasting wood cabinetry, built-in appliances, a convenient pantry, and a breakfast bar that's ideal for casual dining. The main bedroom is a tranquil retreat with a spacious walk-in closet and a private bathroom for your comfort and convenience. Additionally, there's a cozy space with a built-in desk that can easily serve as your home office, providing a quiet and productive workspace. Unwind in the serene balcony, where you can relax and enjoy your favorite beverage while taking in the peaceful surroundings. As part of the Preserve at Weaver Creek community, you'll have access to fantastic amenities, including a park and a refreshing pool. Don't wait any longer to make this charming unit your own – it's a wonderful opportunity to enjoy comfortable living in a welcoming community. Make it yours today! There is a solar rebate.
